pullrequest.title: Using interpolate_x sdf value for animation playback speed

content.raw:
PR looks good to me. 

Note my changes in pull request #536 conflicts with this PR but it should be easy to resolve. We can merge this one first, and I’ll port these changes over to my PR.

But first, we’ll need an ign-common3 release for a clean CI build.
